      <title>交易所库存持续上升，铜价跌破 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/copper-rises-on-us-rate-cut-optimism-china-recovery-signs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商担心全球库存大幅增加和美国就业岗位数据疲软，强化了人们对美联储今年将能够降息的预期，铜价跌至每吨 10,000 美元以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/copper-rises-on-us-rate-cut-optimism-china-recovery-signs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 05:26:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
